<item>
            <title>[LU-4777] bad LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_MASK causes the layout lfsck orphan rbtree failure</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4777</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As shown:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;#define LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_SIZE        PAGE_CACHE_SIZE
#define LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_WIDTH       (LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_SIZE &amp;lt;&amp;lt; 3)
#define LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_MASK        (LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_SIZE - 1)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In fact, the LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_MASK should be &quot;(LFSCK_RBTREE_BITMAP_WIDTH - 1)&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
